AD  - Business Administration Faculty, University of Finance - Marketing, 2/4 Tran Xuan Soan, Tan Thuan Tay Ward, District 7, Ho Chi Minh City, Viet Nam
AD  - Information Technology Faculty, Ho Chi Minh City University of Foreign language -Information Technology, Viet Nam
